column99:
Are you ready to roll up your sleeves and available for occasional shifts? 
 We are looking for flexible and hardworking employees for container unloading in Odense and Søndersø. The work will be based on sporadic shifts depending on demand, and it requires you to be ready to take action when needed. 
 Job Responsibilities: 
 
 Unloading containers and sorting goods 
 Loading and unloading goods from containers 
 Ensuring the warehouse is tidy and organized after each task 
 
 Qualifications: 
 
 Good physical condition, as the job involves manual labor 
 Flexibility and availability for shifts at short notice 
 A team player with a positive approach to work 
 
 What We Offer: 
 
 Hourly wages according to the collective agreement 
 The opportunity for flexible, sporadic shifts that fit your schedule 
 A casual working environment with a focus on teamwork 
 Work in Odense, Søndersø, and the surrounding areas 
 
 If you are interested, please apply via the provided link. Applications sent via email will NOT be considered.
